{"tid":938687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知情人士透露，如果川普對自華進口商品加征的關稅飆升，蘋果公司的供應商將考慮從中國轉移iPhone生產線","createTime":"2018-12-12T13:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T22:02:07.000Z","uid":125193,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4958e02f38a22e7f55af89a95c8e1e55e1ab0e","tid":938687,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 知情人士透露，如果川普對自華進口商品加征的關稅飆升，蘋果公司的供應商將考慮從中國轉移iPhone生產線，但這家美國公司計畫暫時按兵不動。<br />\n<br />\n不願公開身份的知情人士說，即使美國對智慧手機加征10%的進口關稅，這家科技巨頭的供應商仍打算堅持使用現有模式。不過他們稱，如果美國總統川普決定適用更具懲罰性的25%稅率，那就必須重新評估。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司的iPhone大部分組件由其組裝合作伙伴鴻海在中國生產，這一銷往全球各地的手機目前幸免於全球最大兩個經濟體之間的貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果長期以來將中國作為其生產基地，組裝從iPhone、iPad到Mac在內的各類產品。該公司的供應鏈現在涵蓋數百家公司，包括諸如鴻海及和碩等大型組裝商。彭博未能在非美國工作時間聯繫到蘋果公司置評。鴻海與和碩不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果的生產合作伙伴在很大程度上受制於這家美國公司的願望。其中一位知情人士表示，搬遷一部分生產合作伙伴所支撐的龐大網絡將很困難，而蘋果公司目前似乎持觀望態度。另一位知情人士表示，蘋果的一家合作伙伴已經在為非iPhone的生產建議備選地點，但蘋果表示現在幾無必要採取這樣的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n報道：供應商調降預測 川普暗示加稅 連環拳下蘋果延續跌勢<br />\n<br />\n原文標題Apple Is Said to Mull Moving iPhone Output If Tariffs Hit 25%<br />\n<br />\n欲联系中文编辑请洽: Jacob Gu jgu3@bloomberg.net<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E8%8B%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%81%9425-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%B0%87%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2iphone%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A-125000766.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%25E9%2581%259425-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%259B%25A2iphone%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B7%259A-125000766.html&d=qB95qSbxLZ8uPmKg0ty22BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=5536b04c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E8%8B%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%81%9425-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%B0%87%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2iphone%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A-125000766.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欲联系记者请洽：Debby Wu 台北 dwu278@bloomberg.net<br />\n<br />\n欲联系英文编辑请洽：Robert Fenner rfenner@bloomberg.net, Edwin Chan、Peter Elstrom<br />\n<br />\nFor more articles like this, please visit us at <a href=\"http://bloomberg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbloomberg.com&d=qB95qSbxLZ8uPmKg0ty22BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=813c9b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a><br />\n<br />\n&copy;2018 Bloomberg L.P."},{"pid":"67c4b71960536779e5dc1d42897ca00ee2e726c0","tid":938687,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"中國又嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c745444cd5f3443ebc3b1b242d5c795857136e","tid":938687,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2823c8d402d48eb6b01860bb17514eb059abac55","tid":938687,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"去印度生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10613de964cb9948227c2df9666471d731155fa7","tid":938687,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"美國兩議員推bipartisan議案 要求參考中興 禁止對所有違反禁令既中國電訊公司賣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/938075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/938075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca4d68